\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24282,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/01\/22\/patience-first-strike-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":40607,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sabr: Reward for patience at first strike is Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 22, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah Almighty says: O son of Adam, if you are patient and restrained at the first shock of calamity, I would not be pleased with any reward for you less than Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1597 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10321,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/12\/15\/affected-dust-riba-usury\/","url_meta":{"origin":40607,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Riba: Time coming when everyone affected by usury","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cA time will surely come upon people in which none will remain but that he consumes usury. If he does not consume it, he will be afflicted by its dust.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 3331 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32180,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/do-not-curse-wind\/","url_meta":{"origin":40607,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Weather: Do not curse wind directed by Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: A man cursed the wind in front of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him. The Prophet said, \u201cDo not curse the wind, for it only acts as it was commanded. Verily, whoever curses anything that does not deserve it, the curse will backfire against him.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32491,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/24\/world-is-cursed-except-ikhlaas\/","url_meta":{"origin":40607,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dunya: Entire world cursed but sincerity to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe world is cursed and everything in it is cursed, except whatever seeks the countenance of Allah Almighty.\u201d Source: Musnad al-Sha\u0304miyyi\u0304n lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 602 Grade: Hasan li ghayrihi (fair due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/40607","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection"